author: arj
msg: Fixed a subtle bug with HttpUtil that was causing BaseURLs to always print as the name of the host as known to the web container, which in default Tomcat deployments (99%) is called "localhost". Rather than rely on the fact that the user's HttpServletRequest will *actually* return an accurate host name, we do a quick, one-time host name resolution lookup just to make sure.
